OL,3,CNHS Trust warns of a #26million
OL,4,Coverspend and needs to take emergency
OL,5,Csteps
OL,7,FThe boss of East Lancashire Hospitals
OL,8,FNHS Trust has warned it is running a
OL,9,F#26million overspend and needs to take
OL,10,Fsteps to 'reduce costs with immediate
OL,11,Feffect'.
OL,13,FIn a letter sent to all members of
OL,14,Fstaff, Chief Executive Martin Hodgson
OL,15,Foutlined a series of savings including
OL,16,Fa freeze on recruitment.
