OL,3,CNHS Trust warns of a #26million
OL,4,Coverspend and needs to take emergency
OL,5,Csteps
OL,7,FHe said the trust was treating the
OL,8,Fcash crisis as "a major incident
OL,9,Fsimilar to our response to Covid" and
OL,10,Fsaid a priority was to "focus on
OL,11,Fdischarges" to reduce bed occupancy.
OL,13,FA range of further measures include
OL,14,Fensuring everything it does is
OL,15,Fappropriately and effectively coded
OL,16,Fand charged, an end to all non-
OL,17,Fessential spending and considering
OL,18,Fscrapping the shuttle bus which takes
OL,19,Fpatients between the Royal Blackburn
OL,20,Fand Burnley General Hospitals
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
