OL,3,CNHS Trust warns of a #26million
OL,4,Coverspend and needs to take emergency
OL,5,Csteps
OL,7,FHis letter says that at the end of
OL,8,FOctober ELHT was overspending by #26m
OL,9,Fand 'we are not seeing any reduction'.
OL,11,FMr Hodgson's comments come after the
OL,12,Fthe trust revealed 15-hour waits for
OL,13,Fpatients at the Royal Blackburn's
OL,14,Faccident and emergency department
OL,15,Ftriggering a 'red alert'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
