OL,3,CNHS Trust warns of a #26million
OL,4,Coverspend and needs to take emergency
OL,5,Csteps
OL,7,FA statement from Blackburn and
OL,8,FDistrict Trades Union Council said:
OL,9,F"The 'overspend' at the trust appears
OL,10,Fto be a good example of how
OL,11,F'efficiency savings' are really a
OL,12,Fsleight of hand expression for
OL,13,Finadequate funding ` you give with one
OL,14,Fhand and then take away with the other.
OL,16,F"It is difficult to know at the best
OL,17,Fof times how to calculate the 'ideal'
OL,18,Fallocation for a service, but the
OL,19,Fsituation gets even worse when what is
OL,20,Fallocated is chipped away at by other
OL,21,Fmeasures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
