OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1734512551
OL,3,CNHS Trust warns of a #26million
OL,4,Coverspend and needs to take emergency
OL,5,Csteps
OL,7,F"Other than the 'go slow' on vacancy
OL,8,Ffilling, it is very difficult to pin
OL,9,Fdown what the trust's 'expenditure
OL,10,Freductions' will actually amount to `
OL,11,Fexcept that the shuttle bus has
OL,12,Fclearly been put in the firing line
OL,13,Fagain.
OL,15,F"It seems to be a classic case of
OL,16,Fbosses picking on something they don't
OL,17,Freally understand the value of because
OL,18,Fthey have never really understood how
OL,19,Fhelpful it is."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
