OL,3,CNHS Trust warns of a #26million
OL,4,Coverspend and needs to take emergency
OL,5,Csteps
OL,7,FBlackburn MP Adnan Hussain, who met
OL,8,Ftrust bosses on Friday, said it was a
OL,9,F"huge area of concern".
OL,11,FHe said: "The issues surrounding the
OL,12,Fhospital are at the forefront of my
OL,13,Fconcerns and I will explore all
OL,14,Fpossible options, with the government,
OL,15,Fin order to bring about the best
OL,16,Foutcomes for the hospital."
